entities.description: Indicator of whether a youth made a plan to kill themselves due to COVID-19.
Youth responses collected on their experience regarding the COVID-19 pandemic.
Categories in which survey responses can fall, such as Yes, No, Bad Data, Don't Know, Refused, Blank, or Legitimate Skip.

relationships.description: Indicates the survey response categories applicable to the youth response regarding COVID-19.
Denotes that the youth's suicide plan due to COVID-19 is part of the broader youth response collected during the COVID-19 pandemic.
